      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, straightforward transportation with plenty of value for the right buyer. This vehicle shows its age and is being offered as a practical, budget-friendly option, but it still presents a solid opportunity as a commuter, work car, or starter project. A smart choice for someone looking to keep costs low while getting into a vehicle from a trusted seller. Priced to move and represented honestly.",
