      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right person? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option that could make a great starter, backup vehicle, or little project for someone handy. If you want honest value without spending a fortune, this is worth a look.",
